{"tid":2347090,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"每年年尾都諗起好多野","createTime":"2020-12-30T18:28:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T21:38:11.000Z","uid":36961,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"703b0936a49a5aa2cfbaaa8d7e4cd8e6994df045","tid":2347090,"uid":36961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T18:28:22.000Z","msg":"每年呢個時候 都會手多執間房<br />\n明明知 執完可能都仲係咁亂<br />\n但都想做番次掃除<br />\n點知睇番啲野 先知道 哦原來時間過得咁快<br />\n小學個本紀念冊 中學同學寫既聖誕卡<br />\nOcamp啲人寫既龜背<br />\n你第一個女朋友送比你既禮物 你第一次整禮物比人整剩既既材料 傷得你最深既人 你傷得最深既人<br />\n一啲已經唔存在唔再同你人生有交集既人同埋事<br />\n雖然係咁 但係你都好唔捨得咁將佢地扔左佢<br />\n永遠都留番一個位擺呢堆野 明知呢啲野係有幾無用 你都唔會扔佢<br />\n可能直到有一日 你會扔走佢地 但唔係依一刻<br />\n因為 你仲未放低到呢啲記憶 或者係自己念舊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 各位新年快樂"},{"pid":"6b88f9f86fb68a94a24535a7935395fdec5ad52c","tid":2347090,"uid":35587,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T18:30:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5249038fd27a3470da61f236a82b9dc8d3e52d45","tid":2347090,"uid":142872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T18:30:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/gun_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15f7d8968cd6ff9f3635d6d89504eb12f3dffb25","tid":2347090,"uid":216610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T18:34:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99c359d45300697d78afb5518a2dd921a2a7ae96","tid":2347090,"uid":24656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T21:38:11.000Z","msg":"有料"}]}